    {
      "gridPos": { "h": 3, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 1 },
      "id": 41,
      "options": {
        "content": "**How to read latency percentiles:**  \n- **P50 (median)** — 50% of records were processed within this time. Represents the typical experience.  \n- **P95** — 95% of records were processed within this time. Flags occasional slowness.  \n- **P99** — 99% of records were processed within this time. Catches rare but severe spikes (GC pauses, Kafka rebalances, DB locks).  \n\nLatency is measured from **`picked_up_at`** (stamped by the connector) to **TimescaleDB insert** in the Sales Consumer.",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "pluginVersion": "10.3.1",
      "title": "",
      "transparent": true,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
